    },
    {
      "id": "6a2931ae00000000007669bb",
      "text": "使い方",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781084590,
      "updated": 1781084590
    },
    {
      "id": "68480d2a000000000042f2ad",
      "text": "\t引き入れ欄に[輪符]を入力（たいていコピペ）して[引き入れ]する",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749552427,
      "updated": 1749552476
    },
    {
      "id": "68480d5d000000000042f2b0",
      "text": "\t\t同時に10個引き入れできる。cf. https://dlt.kitetu.com/KNo.C7C6/88FB",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749552478,
      "updated": 1749552534
    },
    {
      "id": "68480d45000000000042f2af",
      "text": "  [知番]だけでも引き入れできる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1749552453,
      "updated": 1781084581
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2931b100000000007669be",
      "text": "\t引き入れ欄に検索ワードを入れて検索し、検索結果を[引き入れ]する",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781084594,
      "updated": 1781084594
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2931b700000000007669c2",
      "text": "  ここでの検索はよく使う[zatsma.icon][久住哲.icon]",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1781084600,
      "updated": 1781087596
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2930ac00000000007669b6",
      "text": "",
